vernac_cmds: Definition map_between_equal_subsets : forall (A : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A), X =' Y in _ -> X -> Y.
intros A X Y H x.
Lemma subtype_elt_eats_map_between_equal_subsets : forall (A : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A) (H : X =' Y in _) (x : X), subtype_elt (map_between_equal_subsets H x) =' subtype_elt x in _.
Lemma map_between_equal_subsets_inj : forall (A : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A) (H H' : X =' Y in _) (x x' : X), map_between_equal_subsets H x =' map_between_equal_subsets H' x' in _ -> x =' x' in _.
apply Trans with (subtype_elt (map_between_equal_subsets H x)); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (subtype_elt (map_between_equal_subsets H' x')); auto with algebra.
Definition Map_to_equal_subsets : forall (A B : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A), X =' Y in _ -> MAP B X -> MAP B Y.
apply (Build_Map (Ap:=fun b : B => map_between_equal_subsets H (X0 b))).
red in |- *; simpl in |- *; red in |- *.
Lemma subtype_elt_eats_Map_to_equal_subsets : forall (A B : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A) (H : X =' Y in _) (b : B) (M : Map B X), subtype_elt (Map_to_equal_subsets H M b) =' subtype_elt (M b) in _.
Lemma Map_embed_eats_Map_to_equal_subsets : forall (A B : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A) (H : X =' Y in _) (M : Map B X), Map_embed (Map_to_equal_subsets H M) =' Map_embed M in _.
Lemma Map_to_equal_subsets_inj : forall (A B : Setoid) (X Y : part_set A) (H H' : X =' Y in _) (f g : Map B X), Map_to_equal_subsets H f =' Map_to_equal_subsets H' g in _ -> f =' g in MAP _ _.
unfold Map_to_equal_subsets in |- *; simpl in |- *; unfold Map_eq in |- *; simpl in |- *; unfold subtype_image_equal in |- *; simpl in |- *.
apply map_between_equal_subsets_inj with Y H H'; auto with algebra.
simpl in |- *; red in |- *; simpl in |- *.
Definition cast_to_subset_fun : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A), (forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) -> (B -> W:Type).
Lemma cast_doesn't_change : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A) (H : forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) (i : B), subtype_elt (cast_to_subset_fun H i) =' v i in _.
Definition cast_map_to_subset : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A), (forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) -> MAP B W.
apply Trans with (v x); auto with algebra.
apply Trans with (v y); auto with algebra.
Lemma cast_map_to_subset_doesn't_change : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A) (H : forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) (i : B), subtype_elt (cast_map_to_subset H i) =' v i in _.
Lemma Map_embed_cast_map_to_subset_inv : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A) (H : forall i : B, in_part (v i) W), Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H) =' v in _.
Lemma Map_embed_eats_cast_map_to_subset : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (v : MAP D B) (H : forall i : D, in_part (Map_embed v i) C), Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H) =' Map_embed v in _.
Lemma seq_castable : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A), (forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) -> exists w : MAP B W, Map_embed w =' v in _.
Lemma subset_seq_castable : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (v : MAP D B) (H : forall i : D, in_part (Map_embed v i) C), exists w : MAP D C, Map_embed w =' Map_embed v in _.

Lemma cast_seq_nice : forall (A B : Setoid) (v : MAP B A) (W : part_set A) (H : forall i : B, in_part (v i) W) (P : Predicate (MAP B A)), Pred_fun P v -> Pred_fun P (Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H)).
apply Pred_compatible_prf with v; auto with algebra.

Lemma cast_subset_seq_nice : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (v : MAP D B) (H : forall i : D, in_part (Map_embed v i) C) (P : Predicate (MAP D A)), Pred_fun P (Map_embed v) -> Pred_fun P (Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H)).

Lemma cast_respects_predicates_per_elt : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (v : MAP D B) (P : Predicate A) (H : forall i : D, in_part (Map_embed v i) C) (i : D), Pred_fun P (Map_embed v i) -> Pred_fun P (Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H) i).
generalize H0; clear H0; elim P.

Lemma cast_respects_all_elt_predicates : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A) (v : MAP D B) (P : Predicate A) (H : forall i : D, in_part (Map_embed v i) C), (forall i : D, Pred_fun P (Map_embed v i)) -> forall j : D, Pred_fun P (Map_embed (cast_map_to_subset H) j).
generalize H0; clear H0; elim P.
Definition Map_include : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A), included B C -> MAP D B -> MAP D C.
Definition Map_include_map : forall (A D : Setoid) (B C : part_set A), included B C -> MAP (MAP D B) (MAP D C).
